  "instructions": [
    "heat the olive oil in a large paella pan or skillet over medium-high heat.",
    "add the minced garlic and cook for 1 minute, until fragrant.",
    "add the blanched onion and cook for 2 minutes, until translucent.",
    "add the shrimp and cook for 2 minutes, until pink and lightly charred.",
    "add the smoked paprika, saffron threads, chicken broth, and white wine.",
    "bring the mixture to a boil, then reduce the heat to low and simmer for 5 minutes.",
    "stir in the fromage-blanc and cook for 2 minutes, until melted and creamy.",
    "season with salt and black pepper to taste.",
    "cover the pan with a lid and let it rest for 5 minutes.",
    "serve the paella hot, garnished with crushed tortilla and fresh parsley, if desired."
  ],
